title: Trump Tycoon v1.1
description:
Buy low, sell high, get filthy rich. 

Starting with a paltry $150 million inheritance, players must navigate the cut-throat real estate business to build their fortune. 

Leveraging the power of OPM (Other People's Money), players can buy real estate without personal risk. Boost the ego by hurling insults, unlocking even more ego-boosting insults. Declare bankruptcy to advance to the next level.

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.finalboss.ret
